  "title": "Marine Engineer",
  "description": "<ul><li>Assist Boat Captain ensuring that all of the\nboat machinery is running safely and\nsmoothly.</li><li>Design, operate, maintain and repair the\nmechanical systems of boat.</li><li>Ensure the supply of spare parts for the main\nengine.</li><li>Interpret construction drawings in details.</li><li>Travel by the boat on every voyage.</li><li>Work in the engine room where the boilers\nand engines are located.</li><li><strong>Must have at least Certificate of Competency\nClass 3 Marine Engineer Officer and\nCertificate of Endorsement with related\ncertificated compliance with MPA rules and\nregulations.</strong></li><li>Assist in daily loading delivery schedule from\nPenjuru or Marina South Wharve to every\nmother vessel (Products of delivery:\nLubricants Oil / Chemical packed in drum, pail\nor IBC)</li><li>At least have one year experience with\nlighterage supply industry.</li><li>Must willing to work long hour comfortable to\nwork on boat.</li></ul>",
